     比如创建eclipse桌面图标：
	$cd Desktop
	$sudo touch eclipse.desktop
	$sudo chmod x+u elipse.desktop      #-rwxr--r-- 1      +x 
	$sudo gedit elipse.desktop
	填入
		[Desktop Entry]
		Version=default
		Comment=Eclipse
		Name=Eclipse
		Exec=/home/keetsky/eclipse/eclipse
		Terminal=false
		Icon=/home/keetsky/eclipse/icon.xpm
		Type=Application
		Categories=Developer;          或=Development
